December 12, 1966
Hr. Ben F. Waple, Secretary
Federal Communications Commission
Washington, D, C. 20554
Dear Sir:
Attached are copies of comments vhich we would like to
file in the matter of FCC Docket No* 14185, File B-FCC
66-1007, 90260 - Revision of FM Broadcast Rules; Particularly
as to Allocation and Technical Standards (Educational FM
Channels)*
Thank you very much.
Sincerely,
C. E. Bussard
Instructor of Radio
CEBisk
